Package Lab3.Compulsory

Class Person

java.lang.Object
Lab3.Compulsory.Person
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Person>, Node
public class Person extends Object implements Node, Comparable<Person>
A class representing a Person which implements the Node interface and the Comparable interface. As members, it has a name object of type String representing the name of the Person and a list of Relationship objects.
